---
layout: base.njk
title: Начало
---

<!-- Hero Section -->
<section class="relative mt-4 container-custom h-screen flex items-center justify-center rounded-[25px] overflow-hidden border-2 border-gray-900 shadow-xl">
    <!-- Video: leave as-is (no pointer-events-none) -->
    <video
        class="absolute w-full h-full object-cover z-0"
        autoplay
        muted
        loop
        playsinline
        webkit-playsinline
        preload="auto"
        data-wf-ignore="true"
    >
        <source src="{{ '/assets/video/hero-video.mp4' | url }}" type="video/mp4">
    </video>

    <!-- Gradient overlay: pointer-events-none so taps pass through -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-black via-black to-red-400 opacity-30 z-10 pointer-events-none"></div>

    <!-- Text/button container: pointer-events-none -->
    <div class="text-center relative z-20 pointer-events-none">
        <h1 class="hero-title text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-6">
            Не е важно каква е колата, а грижата за нея
        </h1>
        <p class="hero-subtitle text-xl md:text-2xl text-luxury-gray mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            Бъди звездата на пътя!
        </p>
        <!-- Re-enable pointer events on the link itself -->
        <a
          href="/rezervaciq"
          class="btn-primary hero-button pointer-events-auto"
        >
          Звънни сега!
        </a>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- About Section -->
<section class="section-padding ">
    <div class="container-custom">
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">

            <!-- Left Text -->
            <div class="space-y-6 about-left">
                <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold">За нас</h2>
                <p class="text-luxury-gray text-lg">
                    Твоята страст към колите е и наша. За нас всеки автомобил е специален. Работим така, сякаш е наш – с внимание, прецизност и страст към съвършенството.
                </p>
                <p class="text-luxury-gray text-lg">
                    Преобразяваме коли, които обръщат глави.
                </p>

                <a href="/za-nas" class="btn-secondary">Научете повече</a>
            </div>

            <!-- Right Images (Bento) -->
            <div class="flex gap-2.5 h-[400px] about-right">

                <!-- Left Large Image -->
                <img
                  src="{{ 'assets/images/washed-car.jpg' | url }}"
                  alt="Луксозна чакалня"
                  class="w-1/2 h-full object-cover border-2 border-gray-900 rounded-l-[25px]"
                  style="box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);"
                />

                <!-- Right Two Stacked Images -->
                <div class="flex flex-col w-1/2 gap-2.5">
                    <img
                      src="{{ 'assets/images/coffee-house.jpg' | url }}"
                      alt="Кафе зона"
                      class="h-[calc(50%-5px)] object-cover border-2 border-gray-900 rounded-tr-[25px]"
                      style="box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);"
                    />
                    <img
                      src="{{ 'assets/images/about-home.jpg' | url }}"
                      alt="Чакалня"
                      class="h-[calc(50%-5px)] object-cover border-2 border-gray-900 rounded-br-[25px]"
                      style="box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);"
                    />
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Services Section -->
<section class="section-padding relative">
    <div class="container-custom">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-8 text-white">Услуги</h2>

        <!-- Optional scroll hint overlays -->
        {# <div class="hidden md:block absolute left-0 top-28 bottom-0 w-10 bg-gradient-to-r from-luxury-black to-transparent z-10 pointer-events-none"></div>
        <div class="hidden md:block absolute right-0 top-28 bottom-0 w-10 bg-gradient-to-l from-luxury-black to-transparent z-10 pointer-events-none"></div> #}

        <!-- Scrollable cards container -->
        <div class="flex space-x-6 overflow-x-auto pb-6 custom-scrollbar relative z-20">
            {% for service in services %}
                <div style="box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);" class="border-2 border-gray-900 service-card relative bg-gradient-to-br min-w-[250px] md:min-w-[320px] from-luxury-black to-black-900 p-4 rounded-[25px] flex flex-col overflow-hidden">

                    <!-- Glow behind image -->
                    <div class="absolute top-4 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-72 h-72 bg-gray-700 opacity-50 blur-2xl z-0"></div>

                    <!-- Image -->
                    <img src="{{ service.image | url }}" alt="{{ service.alt }}"
                         class="service-image w-[98%] mx-auto mt-1 h-48 object-cover rounded-[25px] mb-6 z-10 relative transition-transform duration-300 hover:scale-105 hover:rotate-1"/>

                    <!-- Text Content -->
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-white z-10 relative">{{ service.title }}</h3>
                    <p class="text-luxury-gray mb-2 flex-grow z-10 relative">{{ service.description }}</p>
                    <a href="{{ service.link }}"
                       class="btn-primary bg-luxury-red-500 w-full text-center mt-auto z-10 relative">Звънни сега!</a>
                </div>
            {% endfor %}
        </div>

    </div>
</section>

<!-- Gallery Section -->
<section class="section-padding ">
    <div class="container-custom">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-12 text-white">Галерия</h2>

        <!-- Gallery Container -->
        <div class="relative">
            <!-- Navigation Buttons -->
            <button id="prevBtn" class="absolute left-4 top-1/2 transform -translate-y-1/2 z-30 bg-luxury-red/80 hover:bg-luxury-red text-white p-3 rounded-full transition-all duration-300 shadow-lg backdrop-blur-sm">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                    <polyline points="15,18 9,12 15,6"></polyline>
                </svg>
            </button>

            <button id="nextBtn" class="absolute right-4 top-1/2 transform -translate-y-1/2 z-30 bg-luxury-red/80 hover:bg-luxury-red text-white p-3 rounded-full transition-all duration-300 shadow-lg backdrop-blur-sm">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                    <polyline points="9,18 15,12 9,6"></polyline>
                </svg>
            </button>

            <!-- Gallery Wrapper -->
            <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-[50px] shadow-2xl " style="box-shadow: 0 4px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);">
                <div id="gallerySlider" class="flex transition-transform duration-500 ease-in-out">
                    {% for project in projects.slice(0, 5) %}
                        <div class="w-full flex-shrink-0 relative">
                            <!-- Project Image -->
                            <div class="relative h-[500px] md:h-[600px] rounded-[50px] overflow-hidden border-2 border-gray-900 ">
                                <img 
                                    src="{{ project.images[0] | url }}" 
                                    alt="{{ project.carMake }} {{ project.carModel }} - {{ project.service }}"
                                    class="w-full h-full object-cover"
                                />

                                <!-- Gradient Overlay -->
                                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/80 via-transparent to-transparent"></div>

                                <!-- Project Info -->
                                <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 p-8 text-center">
                                    <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-2">
                                        {{ project.carMake }}
                                        {{ project.carModel }}
                                    </h3>
                                    <p class="text-luxury-gray text-lg md:text-xl">
                                        {{ project.service }}
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    {% endfor %}
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Gallery Indicators -->
            <div class="flex justify-center mt-6 space-x-2">
                {% for project in projects.slice(0, 5) %}
                    <button 
                        class="gallery-indicator w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-luxury-gray/40 hover:bg-luxury-red/60 transition-all duration-300"
                        data-slide="{{ loop.index0 }}"
                    ></button>
                {% endfor %}
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- View All Projects Button -->
        <div class="text-center mt-12">
            <a href="/proekti" class="btn-secondary">
                Вижте цялата галерия
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Testimonials Section -->
<section class="home-testimonials section-padding ">
    <div class="container-custom">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-12">Отзиви от клиенти</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            <!-- Testimonial 1 -->
            <div style="box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);" class=" bg-gradient-to-br from-luxury-black to-luxury-black/80  p-8 rounded-[25px] border-2 border-gray-900">
                <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-luxury-red rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-xl font-bold">ИП</div>
                    <div class="ml-4">
                        <h4 class="font-bold">Иван Петров</h4>
                        <p class="text-luxury-gray">Мерцедес S-класа</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <p class="text-luxury-gray">Отношението и вниманието към детайла са на топ ниво! Колата ми блести като нова след тяхната грижа.</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Testimonial 2 -->
            <div style="box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);" class=" bg-gradient-to-br from-luxury-black to-luxury-black/80  p-8 rounded-[25px] border-2 border-gray-900">
                <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-luxury-red rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-xl font-bold">МГ</div>
                    <div class="ml-4">
                        <h4 class="font-bold">Мария Георгиева</h4>
                        <p class="text-luxury-gray">БМВ X5</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <p class="text-luxury-gray">Керамичното покритие направи чудеса! Автомобилът ми е защитен и изглежда невероятно. Препоръчвам!</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Testimonial 3 -->
            <div style="box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);" class=" bg-gradient-to-br from-luxury-black to-luxury-black/80  p-8 rounded-[25px] border-2 border-gray-900">
                <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-luxury-red rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-xl font-bold">ГД</div>
                    <div class="ml-4">
                        <h4 class="font-bold">Георги Димитров</h4>
                        <p class="text-luxury-gray">Ауди A6</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <p class="text-luxury-gray">Професионализъм и страст към работата. Детайлингът беше перфектен, а безплатният оглед много помогна!</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- FAQ Section -->
<section class="section-padding">
    <div class="container-custom">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-12">Често задавани въпроси</h2>
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-4">
            <!-- FAQ Item 1 -->
            <div style="box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);" class="bg-gradient-to-br from-luxury-black to-luxury-black/80 p-6 rounded-2xl border-2 border-gray-900">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Какво включва безплатният оглед?</h3>
                <p class="text-luxury-gray">Безплатна оценка на състоянието на автомобила Ви. Ще обсъдим нуждите му и ще Ви предложим най-доброто и изгодно решение.</p>
            </div>

            <!-- FAQ Item 2 -->
            <div style="box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);" class="bg-gradient-to-br from-luxury-black to-luxury-black/80 p-6 rounded-2xl border-2 border-gray-900">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Колко време отнема керамичното покритие?</h3>
                <p class="text-luxury-gray">Нанасянето на керамично покритие обикновено отнема между 4 и 8 часа, в зависимост от състоянието на автомобила и избраното покритие.</p>
            </div>

            <!-- FAQ Item 3 -->
            <div style="box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);" class="bg-gradient-to-br from-luxury-black to-luxury-black/80 p-6 rounded-2xl border-2 border-gray-900">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Какво прави детайлинга различен?</h3>
                <p class="text-luxury-gray">Малките детайли правят голямата разлика. Всеки сантиметър от автомобила Ви ще бъде обработен с прецизност, без компромиси.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- CTA Section -->
<section class="section-padding relative">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10 z-10"></div>

    <div class="container-custom text-center relative z-20">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Готови ли сте за луксозно изживяване?</h2>
        <p class="text-luxury-gray text-lg mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Нашата мисия е да направим автомобила Ви да изглежда по-добре от всякога. Работим, за да сте 100% доволни от резултата.</p>
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
            <a href="/rezervaciq" class="btn-primary">Звънни сега!</a>
            <a href="/kontakt" class="btn-secondary">Свържете се с нас</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<script src="{{ '/assets/js/home-gallery.js' | url }}" defer></script>
